00:00:44.309 --> 00:00:49.128
this new input of 5, is we substitute it in to all the places where we see x in

00:00:49.128 --> 00:00:53.987
the expression on the right hand side over here. So, in fact the first term you

00:00:53.987 --> 00:00:57.556
