00:01:02.283 --> 00:01:06.992
that f of 5 is equal to 5 minus 3. We can evaluate this to see that f of 5 is

00:01:06.992 --> 00:01:12.514
equal to 2. So 5 here is our input, and when plugged in to this function, the

00:01:12.514 --> 00:01:18.052
